public java.lang.String toString()

Overrides:
toString in class java.lang.Object

The format is as following example: List of the properties for Alliance ,taxID: 1235 ______________________________________________________ Property Name : Belmar Located in Silver Spring Belonging to:John Smith Rent Amount: 1200.0 Property Name : Camden Lakeway Located in Rockville Belonging to:Ann Taylor Rent Amount: 2450.0 Property Name : Hamptons Located in Rockville Belonging to:Rick Steves Rent Amount: 1250.0 ______________________________________________________ total management Fee: 294.0
